{"tid":1478432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[垃撚圾] 香港獸醫護士學會","createTime":"2019-08-16T13:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T13:45:47.000Z","uid":280926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ca62a32a92e326511c34b357822079f5c97e3e","tid":1478432,"uid":280926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:45:47.000Z","msg":"香港獸醫護士學會係facebook (現已del group)發咗編聲明。<br />\n<br />\n聲明內容竟然話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會就近期發生嘅事作聲明</span></strong>(係咩玩法)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾成班獸醫護士圍屌後就del post del group<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個垃圾學會，從來無為過同行爭取權益，無爭取獸醫護士考牌制度，淨係識每個月派埋啲垃圾月刊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cxBQkCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcxBQkCY.jpg&h=a4ecb2e0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}